      "message": "What do you suggest instead? CompileAndAttachShader? What I like about using the exact name in theory is that it should make it easy to find using code search. That said, \"CompileAndAttachShader\" only turns up this or code around it, so it should be close enough. Your comment sounds like it might apply to the other trace names here, too. Should those change, and if so, to what?",
